                <title>SPECIAL DISCOUNTS</title>
                <p>Bentham Science offers discounts to those corresponding authors who are based in low-income countries*.</p>
                <p>The authors who wish to avail this offer should request for a discount at the time of submission of their manuscripts to Bentham Science.</p>
                <sec>
